                        <h2 class="panel-title">FAQ's</h2>
                    </header>
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <div class="panel-group faq" id="accordion">
                                <div class="panel panel-accordion detail-plan">
                                    <div class="panel-heading">
                                        <h4 class="panel-title">
                                            <a class="accordion-toggle collapse in collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#bulk">
                                                Material Master-BulkUpload
                                            </a>
                                        </h4>
                                    </div>
                                    <div id="bulk" class="accordion-body collapse">

                                        <div class="panel-body">
                                            <div class="form-group single-item">
                                                <div class="col-md-12">
                                                    <div class="col-md-12">
                                                        <label class="col-md-3 control-label">Upload File</label>
                                                        <div class="col-md-8">
                                                            <div class="fileinput fileinput-new input-group" data-provides="fileinput">
                                                                <div class="form-control" data-trigger="fileinput"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-file fileinput-exists"></i> <span class="fileinput-filename"></span></div>
                                                                <span class="input-group-addon btn btn-default btn-file"><span class="fileinput-new">Select file</span><span class="fileinput-exists">Change</span><input type="file" name="..." onchange="angular.element(this).scope().LoadFileData1(this.files)"></span>
                                                                <a href="#" class="input-group-addon btn btn-default fileinput-exists" data-dismiss="fileinput">Remove</a>
                                                            </div>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <div class="col-md-1 no-padding">
                                                            <button class="btn btn-primary"align="right" ng-click="UploadFileBulk()">Upload</button>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;

                                                        </div>

                                                        </div>
                                                    <div class="col-md-12 no-padding">
                                                        <div class="flex-row flex-nowrap">

                                                            <div ng-repeat="fle in Folderfiles1">


                                                                <div @*class="col-sm-2"*@ @*style="text-align:left;margin-top:10px;border-left: 1px solid #ccc;"*@>
                                                                    <a ng-show="@Request.RequestContext.HttpContext.Session["show"] == true" ng-click="Remove(fle)"></a>
                                                                    <a target="_blank" href="~/Guideline/{{fle}}" style="color: #000;font-weight: 300;">
                                                                        <div ng-show="fle.substr(fle.lastIndexOf('.') + 1) == 'xlsx'"><img src="~/Images/icon.png" /></div>

                                                                        <h6>{{fle}}</h6>
                                                                    </a>
                                                                </div>


                                                            </div>
                                                        </div>
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>

                                            </div>

                                        </div>

                                 
                                </div>
                                <div class="panel panel-accordion detail-plan">
                                    <div class="panel-heading">
                                        <h4 class="panel-title">
                                            <a class="accordion-toggle collapse in collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#2">
                                                WHAT TYPE OF FILE DOES TOOL ACCEPT AND FORMAT?
                                            </a>
                                        </h4>
                                    </div>
                                    <div id="2" class="accordion-body collapse">
                                        <div class="panel-body">
                                            <div class="col-md-12">
                                                <p><strong>Excel :- xls,xlsx</strong></p>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="panel panel-accordion detail-plan">
                                    <div class="panel-heading">
                                        <h4 class="panel-title">
                                            <a class="accordion-toggle collapse in collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#3">
                                                HOW TO DOWNLOAD OVERALL DUMP DATA?
                                            </a>
                                        </h4>
                                    </div>
                                    <div id="3" class="accordion-body collapse">

                                        <div class="panel-body">
                                            <div class="col-md-12">
                                                <p>
                                                    <strong>
                                                        Overall dump data can be downloaded with respect to,<br />a.	Date modified: report > export > role > username > status (pending), by selecting the role of the user and name with respect to the file status and date, and even with the option of display fields in the downloaded excel format.
                                                        <br />b.	Without date modified: when selected without date, overall uploaded existing files in prosol can be downloaded
                                                    </strong>
                                                </p>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <div class="panel-group faq" id="accordion">
                                <div class="panel panel-accordion detail-plan">
                                    <div class="panel-heading">
                                        <h4 class="panel-title">
                                            <a class="accordion-toggle collapse in collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#15">
                                                HOW ARE UOM SETTED IN TOOL?
                                            </a>
                                        </h4>
                                    </div>
                                    <div id="15" class="accordion-body collapse">

                                        <div class="panel-body">
                                            <div class="col-md-12">
                                                <p>
                                                    <strong>
                                                        1: In Prosol the UOM or Unit of Measure can be fixed with respect to Noun Modifier as Base UOM or against Characteristic Attribute.
                                                        <br /> i)	Base UOM: Data Dictionary > Create Template > Giving input Noun and Modifier
                                                        <br /> ii)	Attribute UOM: Can be added in Two Ways
                                                        <br /> a.	Against Noun Modifier: Data Dictionary > Create Template > Giving input Noun and Modifier > Selecting Attributes > Add UOM
                                                        <br /> b.	Bulk Upload: Data Dictionary > Create Template > UOM Bulk Upload
                                                        <br />
                                                        <br />
                                                        2: New UOM can also added to Prosol in
                                                        Material Master > Tools > Settings > Attribute UOM

                                                    </strong>
                                                </p>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="panel panel-accordion detail-plan">
