                                            <a class="accordion-toggle collapse in collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#16">
                                                HOW TO UPLOAD BULK VENDOR LIST?
                                            </a>
                                        </h4>
                                    </div>
                                    <div id="16" class="accordion-body collapse">

                                        <div class="panel-body">
                                            <div class="col-md-12">
                                                <p><strong>Vendors Can Be Uploaded In Bulk From Material Master > Tools > Vendor Details > Bulk Upload > By Downloading The Excel Template</strong></p>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="panel panel-accordion detail-plan">
                                    <div class="panel-heading">
                                        <h4 class="panel-title">
                                            <a class="accordion-toggle collapse in collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#17">
                                                HOW TO CREATE NEW UOM AGAINST ATTRIBUES AND WHO IS RESPONSIBLE TO CREATE?
                                            </a>
                                        </h4>
                                    </div>
                                    <div id="17" class="accordion-body collapse">
                                        <div class="panel-body">
                                            <div class="col-md-12">
                                                <p>
                                                    <strong>
                                                        a. New UOM can be created from Material Master > Tools > Settings > Attribute UOM
                                                        <br />b.	Only Admin can create New UOM
                                                    </strong>
                                                </p>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
</form>
